works.description:
This is Dhanlaxmi Kuber Dhanwarsha Yantra
 
kit, for financial problem, money, income, job problems, business
problems,  
in family matters and in all kind of financial problems and materialistic 

problems. In this you will get a Key of Money which you will keep in your 

money locker, also one small magical key of money u will keep in business 

place. That key opens the door of money for you from different channels
and  
sectors in life, it will remove all bad luck and increase good luck. This 

is real key which is energized with Mahalaxmi and Kuber Maha mantra. That 

items are very strong and specially to open door of money and wealth  
prosperity in life. Enough money will come which is unexpected for anyone 

who is facing lot of financial troubles in life.

One murti of Lord Kuber and Maa Laxmi energized you will keep at your  
business place or at home where you can do daily worship for it. From this
 
worship and energized murti Mahalaxmi and Kuber will live in your home and
 
at business place permanently and flow money and wealth there always.

Also One turtle is there which is energized with Genie mantra, whenever
you  
have any wish write on the paper, put under turtle plate also fill water  

into bowl. your wish will be done before water will dry. Also there is Two
 
Sri yantra which you will hang at home also in office also you can wear it
 
for best result. That sri yantra is fully energized and it attracts money 

day by day and increase happiness and peace in life with wealth. Also two 

lockets are there which you will wear in neck. also the person who is  
earning money for home that person should wear second locket in neck.Also 

free CD avaialble in packet in which some mantra and Mahalaxmi mantra  
included, you should play it daily and listen with full devotion and
faith.

You can taken loan, business not going good, you are struggling for job,  

your all works, try failed, not getting success, govt sector problem,
Court  
case or family matters you have so purchase this kit and use it within 31 

days everything will be normal and in whole life you will not face such  
type of problem again.

Cost- 1900 RS INR
